snippet.title: Project Unknown Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2115390/Project_Unknown/

PROJECT UNKNOWN is a 1-4 online co-op horror game filled with immersive horror phenomena and complex mechanics. Exorcise different ghosts, utilize a variety of tools, and pick the character that most suits you!
